{"id":165014,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/07/译者-《译者》每日原文推荐-201171/","date":"2011-07-02T03:30:22Z","modified":"2011-07-03T14:56:12Z","title":"译者 | 《译者》每日原文推荐  2011/7/1","content":"<p><p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以下为每日原文推荐。如果你有兴趣，请参与翻译并将译文寄给</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《译者》</span></a><b>(</b><span><b><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"mailto:iyizhe@gmail.com\"><span>iyizhe@gmail.com</span></a>)</span></b></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以便与大家共享。欢迎使用</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feedburner.google.com/fb/a/mailverify?uri=yizhe&#038;loc=en_US\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">邮件组</span></a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">、</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://goo.gl/f1NDK\">Google Reader</a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">和推特（</span><span><span>@yigroup, @xiaomi2020</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）跟踪我们的最新消息。</span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【时政热点】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国法律与政策博客</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://chinalawandpolicy.com/2011/06/30/ai-weiwei-artist-dissident-and%E2%80%A6-tax-evader/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">艾未未：艺术家、异议者……逃税犯？</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——外国专家根据中国法律分析艾未未的可能命运</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span>Shanghaiist – <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://shanghaiist.com/2011/07/01/newly_released_hivaids_activist_hu.php\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">胡佳接受《南华早报》采访</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“我是自由的，而我的看守们却是不自由的。”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约书评》博客</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nybooks.com/blogs/nyrblog/2011/jun/30/true-confessions/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的政治犯：真的坦白交代吗？</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——从艾未未到胡佳，所谓“坦白交代”跟过去的三叩九跪一样，都是一种仪式而已</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/commentisfree/libertycentral/2011/jul/01/china-human-rights-lawyers-detention-torture\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">谁来保护那些捍卫法律的人？</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国的人权律师们越来越成为被打击的对象。他们需要有人保护。</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/07/02/world/asia/02iht-hong02.html?partner=rss&#038;emc=rss\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">香港一年一度的七一游行显示出不满在增加</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——数万人冒着酷暑参加了这次示威活动</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/environment/blog/2011/jul/01/inner-mongolia-grasslands-degradation-unrest\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">内蒙草原遭到的环境和文化破坏</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——随着矿工和游客涌入那些生态脆弱地区，紧张气氛在升温</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《金融时报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.ft.com/intl/cms/s/0/33c093e4-a363-11e0-8990-00144feabdc0.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">找出中国想要的是什么</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——随着中国的崛起，不仅西方不太清楚到底它想要什么，连它自己可能也不太清楚</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span>Miller-McCune – <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.miller-mccune.com/politics/whose-road-led-to-hus-china-33126/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">胡锦涛走的是谁的路？</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——毛泽东？邓小平？还是……孔老二？</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">北京见红</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://seeingredinchina.com/2011/07/01/red-songs-red-banners-red-olympics-but-where-is-the-heart/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">红歌、红旗、红色奥运……可是，红心在哪里？</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——美国可以放心，中国不会再来一次文革</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《外交政策》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.foreignpolicy.com/articles/2011/06/30/chairman_maos_technicolor_dream_world\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【图说】毛泽东时代的彩色世界</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——新中国的宣传画回顾，社会主义天堂？幻境？</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《外交政策》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.foreignpolicy.com/articles/2011/07/01/aint_no_party_like_the_communist_party?page=0,22\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【图说】与众不同共产党</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中共老照片集，包括现在大陆不会再见到的照片</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《外交政策》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blog.foreignpolicy.com/posts/2011/07/01/for_love_of_party\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">爱党还是爱热闹？</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中共的九十周年庆祝有点奇怪，而这不仅仅是因为九十这个数字有点老朽的味道</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国外人</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://chinabystander.wordpress.com/2011/07/01/the-battle-behind-the-birthday-for-a-billion/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">党的生日背后的战争</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——党的下一代领导人将是出生在</span><span>1949</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年之后的第一代，他们的立场对中国今后的趋势至关重要</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/gallery/2011/jul/01/china-anniversary-communist-party-in-pictures#/?picture=376376834&#038;index=17\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【图说】中国庆祝中共建党</span>90<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">周年</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——给毛主席擦鼻子的照片有木有？这个有！</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">花岗斋杂记</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://granitestudio.org/2011/07/01/its-a-mad-mad-90th-anniversary/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">疯狂的九十周年</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——今年夏天的两件大事：中共的</span><span>90</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">岁生日和《广告狂人》暂停新季。这两者之间有些奇妙联系</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《大西洋》月刊</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.theatlantic.com/international/archive/2011/07/90-years-of-the-chinese-communist-party/241055/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中共建党九十周年</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中共显然已经不再是个革命党，但它的统治还能再延续十年吗？</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span>MSNBC – <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://behindthewall.msnbc.msn.com/_news/2011/07/01/6987868-chinas-communist-party-marks-90th-birthday\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">在延安看中共建党</span>90<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">周年</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——记者在革命摇篮的一所干部培训学校里的所见所闻</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span>MSNBC – <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://behindthewall.msnbc.msn.com/_news/2011/07/01/6990753-communist-party-embraces-90th-birthday-but-not-all-chinese-do\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中共庆祝建党</span>90<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">周年，但不是所有中国人都感到高兴</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——在党的生日这天，美国使馆签证处前依然排着长队。</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">布鲁金斯研究所</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.brookings.edu/opinions/2011/0630_china_communism_shambaugh.aspx?rssid=china&#038;utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+BrookingsRSS%2Ftopics%2Fchina+%28Brookings%3A+Topics+-+China%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中共建党</span>90<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">周年</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中共在七一前夕再次公布修改过的党史。然而，它对历史依然做了选择性的回避</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业周刊》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.businessweek.com/news/2011-07-01/communists-embrace-in-the-black-over-red-book-as-party-is-90.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">党已</span>90<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">岁，但还在吸引年轻人</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“我入党是因为今后找工作时会有所帮助。”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.wsj.com/chinarealtime/2011/07/01/a-notable-no-show-at-communist-partys-90th-birthday/?mod=WSJBlog\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中共</span>90<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年庆典上引人注目的缺席者</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——江泽民的缺席助长了近些月来关于他健康变差的谣言，并因此失去了对党内关键决策的影响。</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.wsj.com/chinarealtime/2011/07/01/how-to-update-the-communist-partys-90-year-old-propaganda/?mod=WSJBlog\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">如何让中共</span>90<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">岁的宣传手段焕发新春</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——尽管中国经济有了巨大的变化，党的宣传手段却基本没有任何长进</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/07/02/world/asia/02china.html?partner=rss&#038;emc=rss\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">党的庆生会跟党一样纪律严明</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——当中央大员正襟危坐时，地方的庆祝活动却包含了红色脱衣舞</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2011/jul/01/chinese-president-corruption-communist-party\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中共总书记胡锦涛在建党纪念会上的警告</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——他说如果不能有效处理腐败，党就会失去人民的支持</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《外交政策》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.foreignpolicy.com/articles/2011/06/30/what_a_long_strange_march_it_s_been\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">一场奇特的长征</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——十种方法教你判断中共历史既非恐怖片，也非童话剧。</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《外交政策》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blog.foreignpolicy.com/posts/2011/06/30/is_google_censored_in_china_not_so_fast\">Google+<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">被中国封了吗？结论下得太早了</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——《泰晤士报》和《华盛顿邮报》关于</span><span>Google+</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">被封的报道有误</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">外交学者</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://the-diplomat.com/china-power/2011/07/01/chinas-perception-vacuum/?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+the-diplomat+%28The+Diplomat+RSS%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的认知真空</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国对自己形象的看法，与周边国家对它的认知有着显著差距。如果不解决这种落差，矛盾不可避免</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【经贸动向】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/07/01/us-usa-apparel-manufacturing-idUSTRE7602DT20110701\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">洛杉矶服装业公司因成本原因从中国撤回</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“时装隔</span><span>10</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">个星期就换，每次从中国做上万件的货，无法应付这个需求。”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美联社</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20110701/ap_on_bi_ge/as_china_oil_spills\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国调查渤海石油泄漏事件</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中海油的油井六月里两次发生泄漏，目前事件正在调查当中</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【社会百态】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《洛杉矶时报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.latimes.com/news/nationworld/world/la-fg-china-train-20110701,0,7394150.story\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">有了子弹头列车，中国感觉像个老大</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——对于中国来说，告诉铁路网就像当年美国的太空计划</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《时代》周刊</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.time.com/time/world/article/0,8599,2080443,00.html?xid=rss-world&#038;utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+time%2Fworld+%28TIME%3A+Top+World+Stories%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的同性恋人士反击网络言论审查</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“豆瓣”网站对同性恋言论的审查引起北京同性恋人士的抗议</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">北京休闲</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.timeoutbeijing.com/features/Around_Town/12248/Red-Beijing.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">北京五大毛泽东主题场所</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——在党的生日来临之际，老外选出红色主题的五个去处</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国节奏</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.thechinabeat.org/?p=3585\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">红色遗产</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——重庆的红歌舞是出于怀旧、爱国、找乐、还是当真的？</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><i>如果您的iPad可以翻墙，请点击<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\">这里</a>即可看到最新译文；如果您的iPhone可以翻墙，请点击<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/?m=1\">这里</a>并加入书签；如果您的电脑可以翻墙，请到<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\">这里</a>的左栏参加我们的一个小调查</i><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5425822223623422432-812234664981988716?l=yyyyiiii.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":682,"categories":[1],"tags":[8840]}